text: Oof. Color matters. There are Six parts to a potential luzak. Stem, Thorns, Petals, Petal spots, flower middle, and what look like strings that grow from the middle. There are three colors. Orange, White and Purple. There can be any amount of anyof these colors except for 2 if there are only 2 orange pieces it is not a luzak. if there are only 2 purple pieces it is not a luzak. if there are only 2 white pieces it is not a luzak.
